lead_paragraph: Ben Evans shot five birdies in his first six holes and finished with a 6-under 65 and a one-shot lead in the opening round of the KLM Open on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Ben Evans Ahead by 1 in KLM Open With 6-Under 65 in Round 1
